        <abstract> 
<p>THH’s catalogue [THH and R. Etheridge, <hi rend="italic">A catalogue of the collection of fossils in the Museum of Practical Geology</hi> (1865), part published in 1857] best <hi rend="italic">résumé</hi> he has seen of science of natural history. On classification he is not quite sure that he wholly goes along with THH. Encloses a few criticisms of THH’s preface.[enclosure survives as copy only].</p> 
